data.description: Beautiful home situated in the desirable Jasmine Hill area!  This home features 4 bedrooms and 3 1/2 baths.  The kitchen is well equipped, has solid surface counters and offers lots of cabinet storage. The living room has a super high ceiling, a fabulous wood burning fireplace and huge windows to provide natural sunlight. The living room flows well and opens to the formal dining room.  The master suite can easily accommodate oversized furniture.  The bath has a great garden tub, a double vanity and a separate shower.  ALL of the bedrooms are a great size with tons of closet space.  No need to run down stairs with your laundry basket.  This home has laundry rooms both upstairs and downstairs.  The seller even plans to leave the washer and dryer in BOTH laundry rooms!  Need some additional functional living area?  You will love the private office that could easily be converted to a study room, playroom or even a movie room!  Ample parking is provided with a 2 car garage and an additional concrete pad attached to the driveway.You will love spending time on the back covered porch.  The lot is filled with mature trees and SO MUCH wildlife!  This neighborhood is full of 1-7 acre lots, so plenty of space for all while being just minutes from Wetumpka, Montgomery, Prattville, I-65 and I-85.  Contact your favorite real estate agent and make this Wetumpka home yours today!
